Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier  而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.27,0:00:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.47,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.15,0:00:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角  追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.62,0:00:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.52,0:00:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.26,0:00:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.21,0:00:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.74,0:00:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.31,0:00:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.68,0:00:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.25,0:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.82,0:01:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.36,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.77,0:01:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.14,0:01:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.39,0:01:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟這個男人一起拍照有這麼快樂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.56,0:01:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家的表情都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.23,0:01:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他正如其名是難民的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.50,0:01:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本我們這邊不是叫他久世英雄而是叫他「朗」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.77,0:01:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.11,0:02:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時像「狼」一般無情兇殘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.95,0:02:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時像晴天般晴「朗」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.35,0:02:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是又像不知何時會到處遊蕩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去蹤影的流「浪」漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.82,0:02:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此難民們這麼稱呼他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.58,0:02:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,＃17  修好母子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,台灣當局也是到最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.69,0:02:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才注意到這個男子的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民跟地方角頭達成共識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.79,0:02:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始在馬路上走動的時候出現奇怪的傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.30,0:02:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「有一個能領導難民像是指導者一般的男子」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛開始只是這樣的傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不久之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民們開始頻頻犯下走私案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.84,0:03:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且出現跟地方角頭之間有組織的抗爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.08,0:03:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逼著我們有必要去調查那個傳言的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是確認了久世的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.19,0:03:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛開始還以為這樣很好\N至少難民不會惹是生非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果卻大傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.46,0:03:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們到最近為止還不過是船民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在卻不論在與陸地的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或是跟角頭之間的抗爭方式上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.74,0:03:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都一口氣升級了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這一切的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都在這個男人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我不得不承認他是一個了不起的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.01,0:03:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,C4塑膠炸彈的走私管道也是他建立的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.72,0:03:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用改裝漁船來做海盜行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經是難民的拿手好戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管如此  對我們來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「朗」願意自行離開台灣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是幫了我們一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  對日本公安就得表示哀悼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世離開這裏的理由為何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據那些人所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.01,0:04:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他為了保養義體不得不回日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  是真是假沒人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切合情合理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你  很有參考價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.69,0:04:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於你回程的機票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.03,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不巧今天沒有航班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改明天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.53,0:04:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如你知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.17,0:04:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟大陸的邦交好不容易開始正常化卻出現日美安保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火星飛得到的範圍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.54,0:04:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,常發生有火藥味的事件乃是世上的常態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.31,0:04:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國際線的航班管理也因此無法照原定班表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.22,0:04:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以替繁忙的公安職員擠出休息的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一天就去觀光一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.23,0:05:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.60,0:05:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你不要一個人跑到難民街去閒逛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.23,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這條街已經沒有更多情報了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.27,0:05:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果想調查的話  要往西去大陸旅行看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在各地的難民街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.24,0:05:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說到現在還是四處都有歡迎那傢伙的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.28,0:05:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他實際上並沒有被全世界通緝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不會有人去確認這件事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.67,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.43,0:05:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現在長崎的中樞電腦  我想多半就是久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.37,0:05:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是以這邊的難民來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.87,0:05:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多老人和小孩都沒有電子腦化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.34,0:05:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此  他是如何讓他們跟自己的思考同步呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我在這裏工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是我們的交換條件嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對小孩子也毫不留情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把偷來的東西物歸原主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不叫作交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說  東西在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東西在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.75,0:06:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.26,0:06:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.19,0:07:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你負責到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.59,0:07:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,負責？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.53,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那群人叫作「小傑幫」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這附近的新興幫派角頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做了那種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.14,0:07:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們不是會回來做更嚴厲的報復嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明不是我做的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說我靜靜地看你的手被砍下來比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從某個角度來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你就去道歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次光一隻手可能解決不了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.76,0:07:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這是在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算恩將仇報嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐姐難道是全身義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我第一次看到這種高級貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從哪裏來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.25,0:08:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決定以後要像「朗」那樣換成全身義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.82,0:08:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不過是少一條手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本不覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.09,0:08:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「朗」？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認識「朗」？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問問題的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.46,0:08:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底想幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.93,0:08:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是想請你負責到底而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.64,0:08:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.44,0:08:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  快點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.78,0:08:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.07,0:09:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.84,0:09:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,模型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.91,0:09:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊是絕種動物EX系列的青海龜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.64,0:09:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊是EW系列的鴕鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得很不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來就等上色之後出貨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是大戰前製作的真品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟真品比較起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎麼做  塗色上總有點粗糙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.16,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小地方的細節也會被塗壞掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.83,0:09:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  上面有刻印和型號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來幾乎就像真品不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.87,0:09:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.17,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這全都是可卡因做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用壓力成型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說是以前墨西哥一帶常用的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.65,0:09:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是這種模型  就算大人帶著也不奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想出來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.22,0:10:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是「朗」想出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然這是第一次實際進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼做是想讓我分享重大秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,硬拉我進來當同夥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.47,0:10:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐姐不可能是「小傑」或「黃龍」的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.48,0:10:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是既不是難民也不是普通的旅客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.81,0:10:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要弄到全身義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你說不定知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.95,0:10:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非法弄到那種義體的渠道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.26,0:10:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你弄到全身義體想做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想繼承「朗」想做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼嘛  這種時候打來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊  多謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會躲到某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也消失一陣子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙都是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.41,0:10:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會注意到這是什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.02,0:11:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小傑幫那些人好像找到這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.76,0:11:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我想像中更氣派呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  為什麼到這種地方來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.13,0:11:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去我藏身的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏比那種地方安全多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我頂樓的套房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,套房嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白金卡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐姐你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.07,0:12:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們家的教育方針就是不讓小孩叫我媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我媽媽很年輕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛跟日本進行的會談當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.35,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日美安保締結後的美軍駐軍問題成為焦點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.79,0:12:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日方的回應…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.29,0:12:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然現在鴕鳥只飼養來食用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.09,0:12:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過到本世紀初為止  它們還像這樣奔馳在草原上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護小鳥不受天敵傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,族群中最強的母鳥會收養所有的小鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.87,0:13:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你接下來打算怎麼辦\N把別的小鳥放在自己的小鳥旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.57,0:13:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借此留下最強的基因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.81,0:13:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被期待太多我會很傷腦筋  所以把話說在前頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明天早上就要離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會害你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去跟警察說明清楚  請他們保護你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.63,0:13:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰會保護一個難民的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民在這世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管哪裏都沒有容身之處不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不過是給你們資產階級吃的鴕鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「朗」這麼教你的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.15,0:13:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在這裏是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.98,0:13:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既是英雄也是神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他建議你義體化的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  要做跟「朗」一樣的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也必須義體化才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.26,0:13:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是年輕莽撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.70,0:14:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「朗」說他自己在很久以前就已經死過一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.10,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以剩下的靈魂之火要替理解自己的人燃燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.11,0:14:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對一切絕望的我來說  這句話彷彿給了我希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是復製品也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人有全部模仿的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.65,0:14:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像連電子腦化都沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.22,0:14:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼跟他的思考同步化的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡單啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要跟「朗」說話就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.73,0:14:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要跟他談過一次  大家都會喜歡上「朗」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是奇特的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.87,0:14:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最初見到你的時候  覺得你跟「朗」很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才會找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.98,0:14:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要一個人做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「朗」也都是一個人戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.55,0:14:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨你高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.92,0:14:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.57,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以問你一個問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.71,0:15:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全身義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以做愛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想試試看嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是不要好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.78,0:15:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ID卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車子來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.55,0:16:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.92,0:16:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請開到機場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到那傢伙挺有骨氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對久世的形象也瞭解了一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.68,0:17:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正吸引他們的因素是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.55,0:17:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是Stand Alone Complex的一種嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕得上飛機嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.45,0:17:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對來得及的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.66,0:17:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.17,0:17:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本還是個愛撒嬌的小鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.87,0:17:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司機先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以載我去這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起一件急事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.34,0:17:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次的交易用普通方法行不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我一個人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  如果我沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.72,0:17:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們之中要有人接下這個計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照「朗」教我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以白白犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.56,0:17:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.03,0:17:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩讓我搜查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.13,0:18:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到我還殘留著這樣的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是查？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.73,0:18:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.96,0:19:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感謝您願意聽我冒昧的請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.57,0:19:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦  很有禮貌嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟初次跟您見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.84,0:19:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上以後將會是共同促進生意成功的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.68,0:19:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可還沒決定見你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  真是個有趣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦呢  老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是用這種方式見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.85,0:19:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許有可能成為夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.59,0:19:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不認為嗎  小傑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.89,0:19:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆  您在開玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.03,0:19:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事我們從一開始就沒有想跟黃龍會起衝突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就先殺了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再把同夥的小鬼們也宰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後再來找東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時間我不記得有叫女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不記得你們有叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆  打擾您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能讓難民的血玷污這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.71,0:20:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這份人情我有一天會用別的方式還給您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉我來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始談交易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是昨天的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想用這個交換這孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.96,0:20:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順便也請你們不要對難民報復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要求就這兩項
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果接受  我就會乖乖消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.47,0:20:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是不行我就不得不用武力來逼你們答應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.58,0:20:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少瞧不起人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.18,0:20:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的性子可是很急的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也跟「朗」是同一種人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如您所看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.77,0:21:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.94,0:21:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.52,0:21:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.78,0:21:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人都會被幹掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.46,0:21:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.16,0:21:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要追了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.93,0:21:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知己知彼  百戰不殆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個交易已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.19,0:22:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「朗」應該沒有勸你義體化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.19,0:22:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更沒有要你做幾乎喪命的危險抗爭對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.46,0:22:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有勇氣也有才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.10,0:22:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  死了就什麼都沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.23,0:22:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要放下自傲，才能創造未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.61,0:23:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.29,0:23:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.83,0:23:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.10,0:23:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.60,0:23:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.84,0:23:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字—然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.31,0:23:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省視自身—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.11,0:23:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我—時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.65,0:23:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相  所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.99,0:23:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的—它就在裏面
